      "text": "Color semantics\n• Orange: external context\n• Blue/green/purple: application services & flows\n• Pink: persistence model\n• Violet: route schema entities\n\nArrow verbs\nfetches, upserts, queries,\ninvalidates, dispatches",
      "originalText": "Color semantics\n• Orange: external context\n• Blue/green/purple: application services & flows\n• Pink: persistence model\n• Violet: route schema entities\n\nArrow verbs\nfetches, upserts, queries,\ninvalidates, dispatches",
      "fontSize": 18,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 18,
