      "text": "scheduler.RunNow/Start\n-> CheckExpiry + TryRefresh\n-> SyncStations (krl-station)\n-> SyncSchedules (schedules)\n-> SyncMRTStations + SyncMRTSchedules\n-> Cache.InvalidateAll\n\nNotes: retries, per-station logging, WIB normalization",
      "originalText": "scheduler.RunNow/Start\n-> CheckExpiry + TryRefresh\n-> SyncStations (krl-station)\n-> SyncSchedules (schedules)\n-> SyncMRTStations + SyncMRTSchedules\n-> Cache.InvalidateAll\n\nNotes: retries, per-station logging, WIB normalization",
      "fontSize": 18,
