      "text": "Web /app -> /v1/station\n         -> /v1/schedule/window\n         -> /v1/route/:train_id\n         -> /v1/trip-plan\n\nAPI handlers read-through cache, fallback to DB\nTelegram bot dispatches schedule + weather flows",
      "originalText": "Web /app -> /v1/station\n         -> /v1/schedule/window\n         -> /v1/route/:train_id\n         -> /v1/trip-plan\n\nAPI handlers read-through cache, fallback to DB\nTelegram bot dispatches schedule + weather flows",
      "fontSize": 18,
      "fontFamily": 1,
