      "text": "tables\n• stations(uid PK, id UNIQUE, metadata)\n• schedules(id PK, train_id, station_id, departs_at, arrives_at)\n• bot_users(telegram_id PK, route/time prefs)\n• one_time_alerts(id UUID PK, telegram_id FK, scheduled_for)\n\nindexes\n• schedules(train_id)\n• schedules(station_id)\n• schedules(station_id, departs_at)\n• one_time_alerts(telegram_id, scheduled_for where unsent)",
      "originalText": "tables\n• stations(uid PK, id UNIQUE, metadata)\n• schedules(id PK, train_id, station_id, departs_at, arrives_at)\n• bot_users(telegram_id PK, route/time prefs)\n• one_time_alerts(id UUID PK, telegram_id FK, scheduled_for)\n\nindexes\n• schedules(train_id)\n• schedules(station_id)\n• schedules(station_id, departs_at)\n• one_time_alerts(telegram_id, scheduled_for where unsent)",
