      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1772703997504,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "TrainRoute (key: train_id)\nsource = schedules grouped by train_id\norder = departs_at ASC\n\nRouteStop[] fields\nstation_id, departs_at, arrives_at,\nline, route, origin_id, destination_id\n\nTransferEdge\nroute intersection with wait window 2..240 minutes\n\nPlanner behavior\n1) Prefer direct options first\n2) Else minimal-transfer options\n3) Rank by arrival + transfer quality\n4) Terminal fallback from route-name token mapping",
      "originalText": "TrainRoute (key: train_id)\nsource = schedules grouped by train_id\norder = departs_at ASC\n\nRouteStop[] fields\nstation_id, departs_at, arrives_at,\nline, route, origin_id, destination_id\n\nTransferEdge\nroute intersection with wait window 2..240 minutes\n\nPlanner behavior\n1) Prefer direct options first\n2) Else minimal-transfer options\n3) Rank by arrival + transfer quality\n4) Terminal fallback from route-name token mapping",
